      "name": "network-profile-Customer-A",
      "parameters": {
        "lb_size": "medium",
        "t0_router_id": "82e766f7-67f1-45b2-8023-30e2725600ba",
        "fip_pool_ids": ["8ec655f-009a-79b7-ac22-40d37598c0ff"],
        "pod_ip_block_ids": ["fce766f7-aaf1-49b2-d023-90e272e600ba"]
      }
    }
    ```

    ```
